sources.description:
Neither Bombs, Bullets, Jets or Rockets Can Stop Gorgo...But This Little Boy Knew His Secret!
Greedy sailors capture a giant lizard off the coast of Ireland and sell it to a London circus. Then its mother shows up.

Original title: Gorgo (1961)

Director: Eugène Lourié
Writers: Robert L. Richards, Daniel James
Stars: Bill Travers, William Sylvester, Vincent Winter
Genres: Horror, Sci-Fi
